children.subject: Interesting how they choose their participants through a random lottery

history.content:
Posting on behalf of Hack@Brown at Brown University:

"Hack@Brown 2021 registration is officially open!! Sign up to be part of the 2021 cohort here: https://2021.hackatbrown.org/

Registration closes on January 8th!

Hack@Brown is all about learning. Spend a virtual weekend with 500 other students to take a step out of your comfort zone!

Whether you’re building your first website, dabbling in Photoshop, or hacking with an Oculus Rift, Hack@Brown is for individuals of all backgrounds.

This year, our theme is “After School.” Take inspiration from your passions and experiment with your wildest ideas. Build away!

If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to reach out to the Hack@Brown team at hello@hackatbrown.org and follow us on Facebook and Instagram @hackatbrown!"
